import React from 'react'
import CartItemsTables from '../components/CartItemsTables'
import SubTotal from '../components/SubTotal'
import "../styles/cate.css"

  return (
    <>

        <CartItemsTables />
        <SubTotal />

    </>
  )
}

export default Cart
